    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Clutch pressure control SOL.V. Check"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "523_5.0_jpn_11582144_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Disconnect the coupler (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Cover the coupler with a rag, etc. and be very careful to prevent dust, oil, etc. from entering the coupler."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        {
          "text": "If readings deviate from standard values, check the solenoid wire harness for breaks and shorts, and if the harness is intact Replace clutch pressure control SOL.",
          "refs": [
            {
              "id": "R000529",
              "label": "Replace clutch pressure control SOL.",
              "resolved": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "If readings deviate from standard values, check the solenoid wire harness for breaks and shorts, and if the harness is intact Replace clutch pressure control SOL.",
          "refs": [
            {
              "id": "R000529",
              "label": "Replace clutch pressure control SOL.",
              "resolved": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "If the resistance is within the standard value, proceed to the next step."
        },
        {
          "text": "If the resistance is within the standard value, proceed to the next step."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        {
          "text": "If the solenoid valve operation sound is confirmed, the inspection is completed."
        },
        {
          "text": "If the solenoid valve operation sound is confirmed, the inspection is completed."
        },
        {
          "text": "If you cannot hear the solenoid valve operating, Replace clutch pressure control SOL.",
